  "text": "The monthly SWH presented here was obtained from the ERA-40 reanalysis through the Koninklijk Nederlands Meteorologisch Instituut (KNMI). These data, obtained initially from the original 6-h global fields, were used to elaborate the KNMI ERA-40 wave atlas available at http://www.knmi.nl/waveatlas. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] The horizontal resolution of the global fields used here is 1.5",
